    <p>{`If you init and allocate a struct, it will initialise with some default values.`}</p>
    <p>{`You can also add a "exported" get and set method to help enforce the concept of private variables.`}</p>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-go"
      }}>{`package main

