    <h3 {...{
      "id": "interfaces"
    }}>{`Interfaces`}</h3>
    <p>{`When you have a concrete type, you know what it is and what it can do. An interface is defining what something is but not what it can do.`}</p>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-go"
      }}>{`type FourLegged interface {
    Walk()
    Sit()
}
`}</code></pre>
    <p>{`Implementation in practise`}</p>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-go"
      }}>{`type Part interface {
    Specs() string
    Price() string
}

